# Automatic Server Room Monitoring System

 ## Project Overview
This project is an Automatic Server Room Monitoring System developed using ESP32 and Arduino C Features
- Temperature monitoring using DHT22
- Humidity monitoring
- Voltage monitoring using a Potential Transformer (PT)
- Current monitoring using a Current Transformer (CT)
- Water leakage detection
- 3.5-inch TFT LCD display
- Wi-Fi remote monitoring
- Buzzer alarm for abnormal conditions

 ## Hardware Used
- ESP32 Development Board
- DHT22 Temperature and Humidity Sensor
- Potential Transformer (PT)
- Current Transformer (CT)
- Water Leakage Sensor
- 3.5-inch TFT LCD
- Buzzer

 ## Software Used
- Arduino IDE / ArduinoDroid
- Arduino C++
- GitHub

